snippet.title: Core Keeper - Official Announcement Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2021
snippet.description:
From the developers behind Radical Rabbit Stew comes Core Keeper, an multiplayer adventure game that challenges players to explore and survive an ancient cavern filled with enemies and secrets. Core Keeper is coming to Steam Early Access in late 2021.

#IGN #Gaming #SummerOfGaming
